['t=int(input())

	lad=list(map(int,input().split()))
	lad.sort(reverse=True)
	l1=lad[0]
	l2=lad[1]
	sum=0
	c=0
	for j in range(2,len(lad)):
		if lad[j]<min(l1,l2):
			c=c+1
			if c<min(l1,l2):
				sum=sum+1
	print(sum)']
